{"tid":1610781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"忽發奇想絕對有效「新魔法」","createTime":"2019-10-01T20:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T11:01:51.000Z","uid":175453,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a80476aa2ec0cda6b2ba85ebdcad373fa01ec547","tid":1610781,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:14:40.000Z","msg":"有鑑於RB對自己人既妨礙仲大過狗<br />\n我地係極需要一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陷阱魔法師</span></span><br />\n<br />\n只要將A4 file既其中一面 加上老鼠膠/任何高黏著力產品 另一面加些許油<br />\n就可以令狗隻衝鋒時 一踩中就唔洗再跑 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n優點：<br />\n容易準備<br />\n能即場大量製作<br />\n效果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極佳</span></span><br />\n狗隻解除陷阱需時<br />\n一隻訓低就可以召喚神獸<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n亂拋垃圾<br />\n<br />\n製作方式：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZcDt6gQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZcDt6gQ.png&h=d7db5be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用法：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oDL4EFF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDL4EFF.png&h=186dc3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bade82e720362d930dafe86dd7200ddc3b37621","tid":1610781,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:15:21.000Z","msg":"lm先"},{"pid":"6ef8e65bc89707b58d581ac84c5e130e22d78b5a","tid":1610781,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:15:41.000Z","msg":"有用"},{"pid":"0646418aba3f3d1e1ad294fe04bd24c75ddfe753","tid":1610781,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:16:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e3145dfd058743826ed45e3b69ea30fa9caf2c2","tid":1610781,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:16:19.000Z","msg":"幫手"},{"pid":"5c64d5da68596dd4b6b8de36a56dd5a45d73363c","tid":1610781,"uid":175453,"like":0,"disl